milestones.description: Azharuddin and Ajay Jadeja's 275-run partnership is IND's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 164 between Tendulkar and Vinod Kambli
Azharuddin and Ajay Jadeja's 275-run partnership is the highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 232 between Jonty Rhodes and Cullinan
This is the highest match aggregate (570) involving teams India & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Azharuddin and Ajay Jadeja's 275-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 231 between Tendulkar and Navjot Sidhu
Azharuddin and Ajay Jadeja's 275-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 263 between Inzamam-ul-Haq and Aamer Sohail

stories.title: Tendulkar overhauls Azharuddin's record tally of runs in one-day Internationals
stories.summary: Little master Sachin Tendulkar became the leading run scorer in the one-day internationals during his innings of 69 against New Zealand at Nairobi Gymkhana in the final of ICC Knock Out
